#### A. useTheme.ts (EXISTING THEME HOOK)
**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775475397404-7s6tff/apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts`

